Package: LPI
Title: Statistical LPI Index Estimation Under Parametric Distributions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("Coskun", "Kus", email = "coskunkus@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Fatma", "Zehra Avcioglu", role = "aut"),
      person("Fatma", "Pinaralti", role = "aut"),
      person("Gamze", "Oner", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Provides estimation of LPI-type indices under Gamma, Lognormal and Weibull distributions. 
    The package includes maximum likelihood estimation, asymptotic confidence intervals 
    via the delta method, bootstrap confidence intervals (normal, basic, percentile, BCa), 
    and nonparametric estimators.
